                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Denby</persName></hi>.</head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-09-05"><hi rend="italic">September 5,
                                    1895</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Secretary of the Navy authorizes Barber, naval attaché to Japan, on
                            Chengtu commission. Appoint.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Adee</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Acting</hi></signed>.</closer>
